SOULFUL House Trio, Mi Casa is part of this year’s line up at Smooth FM’s 2nd A Night at the Kazbah Concert. This morning, the stars took time out of their busy Africa Tour to let their Lagos fans know they will be in town in a few weeks’ time. The ‘Jika’ performers alongside The Voice Nigeria winner, A’rese and headliner, South African singer-songwriter and guitarist, Jonathan Butler will trill Lagosians with their electrifying truly authentic African sound. Catch them live at the 2nd ‘A NIGHT AT THE KAZBAH’ concert on the 22nd of October 2016 at The Federal Palace Hotel, Victoria Island, Lagos.

			
